graph TD
    Start([Start]) --> DataColl[Data Collection<br/>Images + IoT Sensor Data]
    DataColl --> DataLab[Data Labeling<br/>Fresh, Early, Moderate, Severe]
    DataLab --> DataPre[Data Preprocessing<br/>Resize, Normalize]
    DataPre --> DataAug[Data Augmentation<br/>Rotate, Flip, Brightness]
    DataAug --> ModelDev[Model Development<br/>CNN / MobileNetV2 / ResNet50]
    ModelDev --> ModelEval[Model Evaluation<br/>Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1]
    ModelEval --> IoTData[IoT Data Acquisition<br/>MQ-135, DHT11]
    IoTData --> PredSys[Prediction System<br/>Image + Sensor Input]
    PredSys --> XAI[Explainable AI<br/>Grad-CAM Visualization]
    XAI --> UI[User Interface<br/>Upload Image & View Result]
    UI --> TestVal[Testing & Validation]
    TestVal --> End([End])

